    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="轮播图的原理"><a href="#轮播图的原理" class="headerlink" title="轮播图的原理"></a>轮播图的原理</h1><p>一系列大小相等的图片平铺，利用CSS布局只显示一张图片，其余的图片隐藏。就是相当于中间有一个div，大小是图片的大小，然后外面有个大的div，包含了所有图片。通过计算偏移量来进行轮播<br>![轮播](轮播图的原理/轮播.png）<br>html代码</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;div id=&quot;container&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;div id=&quot;list&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;1.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;2.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;3.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;4.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;5.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;6.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">&lt;a id=&quot;btnleft&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;左.png&quot; class=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a id=&quot;btnright&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;右.jpg&quot; class=&quot;right&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">&lt;div id=&quot;buttons&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;1.jpg&quot; class=&quot;button&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;2.jpg&quot; class=&quot;button&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;3.jpg&quot; class=&quot;button&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;4.jpg&quot; class=&quot;button&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;5.jpg&quot; class=&quot;button&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;6.jpg&quot; class=&quot;button&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>CSS部分</p>
<p><strong>注意list的overflow:hidden;只显示窗口的一张图片，把左右两边的都隐藏起来。</strong><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">body&#123;</div><div class="line">    padding: 20px;</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">#container&#123;</div><div class="line">	width: 800px;</div><div class="line">	margin: 0 auto;</div><div class="line">	position: relative;</div><div class="line">	overflow: hidden;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">#list&#123;</div><div class="line">	width: 4800px;</div><div class="line">	height: 300px;</div><div class="line">	position: absolute;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">#list img&#123;</div><div class="line">	width: 800px;</div><div class="line">	height: 300px;</div><div class="line">	float: left;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">.left&#123;</div><div class="line">	position: absolute;</div><div class="line">	margin-top: 150px;</div><div class="line">	width: 50px;</div><div class="line">	height: 50px;</div><div class="line">	opacity:0.5;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">.right&#123;</div><div class="line">	position: absolute;</div><div class="line">	margin-top: 150px;</div><div class="line">	margin-left: 750px;</div><div class="line">	width: 50px;</div><div class="line">	height: 50px;</div><div class="line">	opacity:0.5;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">.button&#123;</div><div class="line">	width: 120px;</div><div class="line">	height: 80px;</div><div class="line">	margin-top: 450px;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">.left:hover&#123;</div><div class="line">	opacity:1;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">.right:hover&#123;</div><div class="line">	opacity:1;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>JavaScript部分</p>
<p><strong>先实现轮播效果</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">var list = document.getElementById(&quot;list&quot;);//获取6张图片的div</div><div class="line">var aimg = list.getElementsByTagName(&quot;a&quot;);//获取6张图片</div><div class="line">var btnleft = document.getElementById(&quot;btnleft&quot;);//获取左边的按钮</div><div class="line">var btnright = document.getElementById(&quot;btnright&quot;);//获取右边的按钮</div><div class="line">var abuttons = document.getElementById(&quot;buttons&quot;).getElementsByTagName(&quot;a&quot;);//获取下方的缩略图</div><div class="line">var inow = 0;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">	function move(index)&#123;</div><div class="line">	list.style.left = -index*800 + &quot;px&quot;;</div><div class="line">	if (index &gt;aimg.length-1) &#123;</div><div class="line">		index = 0;</div><div class="line">		inow = index;//这是对于右边的按钮的，防止一直按下去是白屏</div><div class="line">	&#125;</div><div class="line">	if (index&lt; 0) &#123;</div><div class="line">		index = aimg.length-1;//这是对于左边的按钮的，防止一直按下去是白屏</div><div class="line">		inow = index;</div><div class="line">	&#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">	for (var i = 0; i &lt; abuttons.length; i++) &#123;</div><div class="line">		abuttons[i].index = i;//给每个缩略图一个序号，相当于一个数组</div><div class="line">		abuttons[i].onclick = function()&#123;</div><div class="line">			//list.style.left = -800*this.index + &quot;px&quot;;</div><div class="line">			move(this.index);</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">		&#125;</div><div class="line">		</div><div class="line">var timer;</div><div class="line">    function play()&#123;</div><div class="line">	    timer = setInterval(function()&#123;</div><div class="line">		btnright.onclick()&#125;, 1500)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">play();</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这段代码中的move函数，由于不管是轮播还是点击方向键，其本质都是改变div的位置，使它发生位移，从而实现轮播，所以就把它写在了move函数</p>
<p><strong>通过点击方向键改变图片</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">btnright.onclick = function()&#123;</div><div class="line">		inow++</div><div class="line">		move(inow);</div><div class="line">	&#125;</div><div class="line">	btnleft.onclick = function()&#123;</div><div class="line">		inow--</div><div class="line">		move(inow);</div><div class="line">	&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>因为你会发现一直点击下去，会出现白屏，没有图片显示，所以在上面的move函数又增加了一个判断语句，是否图片已经轮播完了，但是我这代码出了问题，点到最后还是会出现一张白屏的，不知道怎么修改。</p>
<p><strong>最后在增加一个功能，就是鼠标放到图片上时，停止轮播，离开又继续轮播。</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">//设置鼠标放到图片上时，停止轮播</div><div class="line">var container = document.getElementById(&quot;container&quot;);</div><div class="line">function stop()&#123;</div><div class="line">	clearInterval(timer);</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">container.onmouseover = function()&#123;</div><div class="line">	stop();</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">container.onmouseout = function()&#123;</div><div class="line">	play();</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>当然这些JS代码要放在window.onload=function(){}中</p>
]]></content>
    
